1 \u0938\u0941\u0930 \u092d\u0942\u092a\u0964\u0964<\/p><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\"><strong>\u092f\u0947 \u0935\u093f\u0921\u093f\u092f\u094b \u092d\u0940 \u0926\u0947\u0916\u0947\u0902<\/strong><\/h5><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/aartis-bhajans-hi\/video-%e0%a4%b9%e0%a4%a8%e0%a5%81%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%be%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%a8%e0%a5%8d%e0%a4%ae%e0%a5%8b%e0%a4%a4%e0%a5%8d%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%b5-2024-%e0%a4%b9%e0%a4%a8%e0%a5%81%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%be\"><strong>Video Hanuman Bhajan: Hanuman Chalisa<\/strong><\/a><\/h5><h5 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\"><a href=\"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/gurus-sants-kathas\/video-kaushik-ji-maharaj-listen-to-this-amazing-hanuman-katha-on-tuesday\"><strong>Video Kaushik Ji Maharaj: \u092e\u0902\u0917\u0932\u0935\u093e\u0930 \u0915\u094b \u0938\u0941\u0928\u0947\u0902 \u092f\u0939 \u0905\u0926\u094d\u092d\u0941\u0924 \u0939\u0928\u0941\u092e\u093e\u0928 \u0915\u0925\u093e<\/strong><\/a><\/h5><p><strong>Hanuman Chalisa in English<\/strong><\/p><p>Doha:<br>Pavanatanaya sankat haran, mangal murati roop.<br>Ram Lakhan Sita sahit, hrday basahu sur bhoop.<\/p><p>Chaupai:<br>Jay Hanuman gyan gun sagar. Jay Kapis tihu lok ujagar.<br>Ram dut atulit bal dhama. Anjani-putra Pavansut nama.<br>Mahavir bikram Bajrangi. Kumati nivara sumati ke sangi.<br>Kanchan baran biraj subesa. Kanan kundal kunchit kesa.<br>Haath vajra au dhvaja biraje. Kandhe moonj janeu saje.<br>Shankar suvan Kesari Nandan. Tej prataap maha jag vandan.<br>Vidyavaan guni ati chatur. Ram kaj karibe ko atur.<br>Prabhu charit sunibe ko rasiya. Ram Lakhan Sita man basiya.<br>Sukshma roop dhari siyahi dikhava. Bikat roop dhari Lanka jarava.<br>Bheem roop dhari asur sanghare. Ramchandra ke kaj sanvare.<br>Laaye Sanjeevan Lakhan jiyaye. Sri Raghubir harashi ur laye.<br>Raghupati keenhi bahut badai. Tum mam priye Bharat-hi sam bhai.<br>Sahas badan tumharo jas gaavain. As kahi Shripati kanth lagaavain.<br>Sankadhik Brahmaadi Muneesa. Narad Sarad Sahit Aheesa.<br>Jam Kuber digpaal jahan te. Kabhi kovid kahi sake kahan te.<br>Tum upkar Sugreevahin keenha. Ram milaye rajpad deenha.<br>Tumharo mantra Bibheeshana maana. Lankeshwar bhaye sab jag jana.<br>Jug sahastra jojan par bhanu. Leelyo taahi madhur phal jaanu.<br>Prabhu mudrika meli mukh mahee. Jaladhi langhi gaye achraj nahee.<br>Durgam kaaj jagat ke jete. Sugam anugraha tumhre tete.<br>Ram duaare tum rakhavaare. Hot na aajanya binu paisaare.<br>Sab sukh lahai tumhari sarna. Tum rakshak kahu ko daarna.<br>Aapana tej samhaaro aapai. Teenon lok haank te kaapai.<br>Bhoot pisaach nikat nahin aavai. Mahavir jab naam sunavae.<br>Nase rog hare sab peera. Japat nirantar Hanumant beera.<br>Sankat te Hanuman chhudavae. Man kram bachan dhyan jo lave.<br>Sab par Ram tapasvi raja. Tin ke kaaj sakal Tum saja.<br>Aur manorath jo koi lave. Soi amit jeevan phal pave.<br>Charo jug parataap tumhaaraa. Hai parasiddh jagat ujiyaaraa.<br>Sadhoo Sant ke tum rakhavaare. Asur nikandan Ram dulare.<br>Ashtasiddhi nav nidhi ke daataa. As var deen Janki maataa.<br>Ram rasayan tumhare paasaa. Sada raho Raghupati ke daasaa.<br>Tumhare bhajan Ram ko paavai. Janam janam ke dukh bisaraavai.<br>Ant kaal Raghubar pur jaai. Jahaan janam Hari-bhakta kahaai.<br>Aur devata chitt na dharai. Hanumat se hi sarba sukh karai.<br>Sankat katai mitai sab peera. Jo sumirai Hanumat balbeera.<br>Jay Jay Jay Hanuman Gosai. Kripa karahu Gurudev ki naai.<br>Jo sat baar paath kar koi. Chhootahin bandi maha sukh hoi.<br>Jo yah padhai Hanuman Chalisa. Hoy siddhi saakhi Gaurisa.<br>Tulsidas sada Hari chera. Keejai naath hriday mahn dera.<\/p><p>Doha:<br>Pavanatanaya sankat haran, mangal murati roop.<br>Ram Lakhan Sita sahit, hrday basahu sur bhoop.<\/p><p><\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>You can read the Hanuman Chalisa here every day. It is written that whoever recites Hanuman Chalisa daily receives the blessings not only of Hanuman Ji but also of Lord Rama and Goddess Parvati. And&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":40,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[105],"tags":[31,33],"class_list":["post-39","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-uncategorized-en","tag-aartis","tag-hanuman-chalisa"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/39"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=39"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/39\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5886,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/39\/revisions\/5886"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/40"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=39"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=39"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dhaarmi.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=39"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}